 event or program.       Alumni Benefits     Art, Music and Theatre         Art, Music and Theatre      Concerts  Gallery 400  Theatre  UIC Radio  Youth Programs        Career and Education         Career and Education      Employment at UIC  Recruiting at UIC  Transcript Request  UIC Alumni Career Services  UIC Extended Campus and Certificate Programs  UIC Graduate and Professional Programs  UIC Online Learning        Civic and Community         Civic and Community      Alumni Awards  College of Business Faculty Expert Guide  Golden Grads Alumni Program  Great Cities Institute  Jane Addams Hull-House Museum  Library Privileges  Local Experts Guide  UIC License Plates        Continuing Education and Lifelong Learning         Continuing Education and Lifelong Learning      College of Applied Health Sciences Continuing Education  College of Pharmacy Office of Continuing Education  College of Dentistry Continuing Education  School of Public Health Continuing Education  College of Medicine Department of Psychiatry  Emergency Management and Continuity Planning Professionals Continuing Education  Center of Excellence in Maternal and Child Health  College of Medicine Social Work Continuing Education  Great Lakes Center (Occupational Health, ENV Health, Children’s ENV Health) Continuing Education        Health and Wellness         Health and Wellness      UIC Alumni Discount at Campus Recreation  Fitness Testing and Personal Training  Illinois Eye and Ear Infirmary  Massage Therapy  Public Dental Clinic  UI Health Family Medicine        Professional Services and Clinics         Professional Services and Clinics      Institute for Leadership Excellence and Development (iLead)  Pro Bono Litigation Clinic  UIC Entrepreneurial Support Program  Veterans Legal Support Center and Clinic        Recreation, Fitness and Social         Recreation, Fitness and Social      Bowling Alley and Bowling Parties  Pool Parties  Rock Climbing/Climbing Parties  Camping and Hiking Gear Rental  Sw